LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:Join composer Karl Brueggemann as he battles against the clock
  to create a (good) Sega Genesis tune in just 55 minutes! To add more pres
 sure\, Karl commits that whatever he creates on this panel stage\, he will
  include on his upcoming FM Synth album High Flyer 2! Gotta compose fast! 
END:VEVENT
