LOCATION:Key Stage/Viking Lounge
DESCRIPTION:Jonathan Aldrich ("jdaster64") is a pianist\, and longtime fan
  of Nintendo VGM (especially the Mario and Kirby series)\, jazz piano\, an
 d the VGM cover scene in general. His inspirations include Brubeck\, Vince
  Guaraldi\, and VGM cover musicians such as the Consouls and the OneUps. 
