SUMMARY:VGM as a Vehicle for Introductory Jazz Arranging
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:Video game music and jazz standards have more in common than o
 ne might initially think! This panel will dive into the shared elements of
  music from those two worlds\, and provide some basic techniques for the n
 ew jazz arranger. 
END:VEVENT
