SUMMARY:Ankylo Tail
LOCATION:Hero Stage/Europa
DESCRIPTION:Ankylo Tail is a jazz fusion band bringing a new energetic twi
 st to VGM classics! Our mission is to take you on a journey - whether you'
 ve heard the tune a thousand times or you've never heard it before\, Ankyl
 o Tail will give you a unique perspective and show you something new. 
