SUMMARY:How to comp for lead instruments
LOCATION:Jam Space
DESCRIPTION:As a horn or woodwind player\, do you ever get tired of sittin
 g idle during other people's solos? Want to help improve the music when yo
 u're not soloing? In this mixed lecture and interactive workshop\, those w
 ho cannot play chords on their instruments will learn tools to contribute 
 to a jam when not playing the melody or soloing. 
END:VEVENT
