SUMMARY:Freeform
LOCATION:Key Stage/Viking Lounge
DESCRIPTION:Jamin and Zeynep are Freeform\, classically-trained musicians 
 who deeply enjoy playing video game music. They play freeform: From pre-wr
 itten arrangements to more jam-session-style semi-improvised pieces\, stre
 tching across a wide variety of genres and styles. 
