SUMMARY:Voicings and Textures: Make Your Music Move!
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:Not sure how to build a chord? Don't know what rhythms to writ
 e? This panel will focus on one of the most overlooked elements of arrangi
 ng: voicings\, the way we choose to stack a chord and build off of it. Poo
 r voicings can muddy an arrangement without you even knowing\, while great
  ones can make it shine. And from there\, we will see how you can turn tho
 se voicings into textures: moving lines for your musicians to perform. Thi
 s step-by-step process will give you a great idea on how to approach your 
 next arrangement\, and could even forever improve your entire music-making
  process! 
END:VEVENT
