SUMMARY:SCORE! Crafting a Complete Soundtrack
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:What makes a great score so moving and memorable? Enjoy an exc
 iting and accessible tour through the building of a would-be-gamescore as 
 we construct musical story from the inside out. Weâ€™ll explore what 
 makes certain melodic choices so powerful\, how to evolve/explode your mat
 erial and how to uniquely support interactive media. Open for absolutely a
 ll\; fans and professionals alike. 
END:VEVENT
