LOCATION:Boss Stage/Regency
DESCRIPTION:Ian Cowell & The Band of Exceptional Goblins has only gotten b
 igger and better since first attending VGM Con in 2023\, and now they’re
  back supporting a new full-length album\, MagicIan! Join them on a musica
