SUMMARY:Inject some life and love into your music videos!
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:After several years of improvement\, I've often been told that
  my music videos feel full of love\, alive\, and engaging. I'm not a profe
 ssional videographer\, so in that light\, this is a presentation of the pr
 actical strategies and methods I've used to get my videos to this point. T
 hese will level up the look and feel of your performances\, and properly c
 onvey the care which goes into making your videos. Examples will include r
 udimentary color grading\, angle selection\, simple movement\, gimbal usag
 e\, and lens selection. Nothing here is advanced\, just simple strategies\
 , easy to understand\, and with huge payoff compared to the effort to lear
 n. 
END:VEVENT
