SUMMARY:The Music Theory of Sick Beats
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:This is going to be a highly educational panel all about rhyth
 ms\, time signatures\, and the sickest beats imaginable. In both my underg
 rad and master's degrees\, as well as spending lots of time studying Sunga
 zer and Tigran Hamasayan music\, I've developed a fascination for highly r
 hythmic based music. I wanted to distill what I know about rhythms into a 
 short 60 minute presentation. Here we are going to break down rhythmic con
 cepts from beginner to advanced\, picking apart songs across video game hi
 story\, and ultimately answering the question that has plagued humanity si
 nce the dawn of time: What truly is the sickest beat? 
END:VEVENT
